description:
This is a Beginner's course for those wanting to learn the basics of Business Branding. Some things we'll focus on are creating a branding strategy, including a name, a logo, and a tagline

The course is about 40 minutes long and all 12 individual lessons are videos. Once the course is over you will surely walk away feeling more equipt and informed on where and how to start the branding efforts for your new or exisiting business.

This course is a compination of lectures and short tests. The student being able to start the branding process with some initial knowledge is the end goal.
title: Brand your Business and Become a Household Name Today.
